                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16850116-4-off20 t16850116-4-cd22"></join> last, and upon his Arraignment, pleading not Guilty he made a general exception in case that any of the jurors should happen to be related to the deceased, which being allowed and twelve new Sworn, Mr. <note>[Text unreadable in original.]</note>ton Councelor at Law opened the case upon the Indictments being a second time read, and then proceeded to call the Witness for the King, and first 
